go_data.term: mitochondrial respiratory chain complex I assembly
go_data.justification: NDUFAB1 copurified with the N-module core subunit NDUFS1 and the N-module assembly factor NDUFA2, suggesting involvement in complex I assembly.
NDUFAB1 is described as an acyl carrier protein.
NDUFAB1 is involved in the assembly of mitochondrial respiratory complex I.
